  286831

  06 Sep 2009; Christian Ruppert <idl0r@gentoo.org>
  -files/50ledger-mode-gentoo.el, ledger-2.5-r2.ebuild, ledger-2.6.1.ebuild:
  Removed unused 50ledger-mode-gentoo.el. Fix repoman complains.

  08 Aug 2009; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> ledger-2.6.1.ebuild,
  +files/ledger-2.6.1-glibc-2.10.patch:
  Fix building with GLIBC 2.10+ wrt #275905, thanks to Arttu Valo for patch.

